This project is part of my basic exercises on OpenCV and Computer Vision.
It demonstrates real-time object detection using the YOLOv8 model (yolov8.pt), capable of detecting persons and 80 COCO dataset classes (e.g., cars, chairs, bottles, etc.).

ğŸ”¹ Key Features

Implemented YOLOv8 with Python and OpenCV

Detects people and other objects from webcam/video/images

Bounding boxes with labels and confidence scores

Lightweight beginner project for practicing object detection

